  "description": "Maximum aggression from OPENSKY — filterReso at 0.7, pitchEnvAmount at 0.5 with fast decay (0.12), shimmer removed entirely. No shimmer, no chorus: raw supersaw storm. Seven unison voices at 0.25 detune — wide, intentionally chaotic. FilterCutoff at 10000 with high resonance creates a self-oscillating edge. PitchEnv at 0.5 gives each note a screaming transient entry. This is solar flare as synthesis: electromagnetic violence.",
